ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="55ccdc2c-2ea2-4430-a9d7-69cd258bf188" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Ingredient Usage" Description="Ingredient Usage with AF/DM Qty and Tons and Cost" CreatedDT="2012-09-07T13:18:07" ModifiedDT="2014-12-31T13:08:47.05" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAlmRA=" ReportVersion="2" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select z.* from ( select hii.InventoryItemName as 'Ingredient' ,hfl.LocationName ,cmp.CompanyName ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AFQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.LargeMeasurementType) as 'AFTons' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'DMQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct, cmp.LargeMeasurementType) as 'DMTons' ,ReportDate = CONVERT(date, it.TransactionDT) ,IsPremix = CAST(case when ISNULL(hi.MadeByRecipeGID, ing.MadeByRecipeGID) is null then 0 else 1 end as bit) ,Cost = it.FifoCost from InventoryTransaction it join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ii.CompanyGID join HistoryInventoryItem hii on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID join HistoryLocation hfl on hfl.HistoryLocationGID = it.FromHistoryLocationGID join Ingredient ing on ing.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID outer apply (select top 1 hi.* from HistoryIngredient hi where hi.IngredientGID = ing.IngredientGID and hi.CreatedDT <= it.TransactionDT) hi where it.TransactionType in (4,8) and hfl.LocationType = 0 ) z where (1=1) </QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
ReportQuery.SQLStatement:
select * from ( select hii.InventoryItemName as 'Ingredient' ,hfl.LocationName ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.LargeMeasurementType) as 'AFTons' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'DMLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct, cmp.LargeMeasurementType) as 'DMTons' ,CONVERT(date, dbo.GetInventoryTransactionReportDT(it.InventoryTransactionGID)) as 'ReportDate' from InventoryTransaction it join HistoryInventoryItem hii on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID join HistoryLocation hfl on hfl.HistoryLocationGID = it.FromHistoryLocationGID
where it.TransactionType = 4 and hfl.LocationType = 0 ) i where (1=1)
